desc_long							评测						“The sharp, professional quality mixed with addictive gameplay and expansive game selection makes Biology Battle quite the bargain.”85% – GameFocus“Novaleaf has created a fully fleshed out game, one that is packed full of replay value and keeps the old school "one more try" spirit alive.”80% – Destructoid												关于这款游戏							In this classic space-shooter, you take the role of a medical nanobot and embark on an exciting journey into the depths of a biological cell. Evade the defense tactics of the other cells and try to survive for as long as possible.Features:Eleven different versus modes (e.g. lasso, froghop, worms)Play online against thousands of real opponentsComprehensive tournament mode and demanding coop modeImprove the ship´s capabilities with various bonusesAdaption of the XBLA-hit						
